Document: VisualShaderNodeParticleMeshEmitter
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodeparticlemeshemitter.rst
Summary: A VisualShaderNodeParticleEmitter that emits particles in the shape of an assigned mesh, from its surfaces.

This node emits particles in the shape of the assigned mesh. Particles are emitted from the mesh's surfaces, either all surfaces or only the specified one. The mesh property determines the shape from which particles are emitted.
